309
00:20:19,568 --> 00:20:22,747
WELL, IT WOULDN'T MAKE A WHOLE
LOT OF SENSE TO QUIT NOW, WOULD IT?

310
00:20:22,771 --> 00:20:25,406
IT IS OF NO SIGNIFICANCE TO YOU

311
00:20:25,474 --> 00:20:29,076
WHAT OCCURS WHEN A DADDY
RUNS OUT ON HIS FAMILY?

312
00:20:29,145 --> 00:20:30,677
I CUT MY TEETH...

313
00:20:30,746 --> 00:20:32,690
HOW WILL YOU LIVE?
ON ITS SIGNIFICANCE.

314
00:20:32,714 --> 00:20:34,581
YOU HAVE NO VOCATION.

315
00:20:34,650 --> 00:20:36,350
DON'T WORRY ABOUT ME.

316
00:20:36,419 --> 00:20:39,686
IT'S MY GRANDCHILDREN
I WORRY ABOUT.

317
00:20:39,755 --> 00:20:42,722
HOW WILL YOU MEET
YOUR SUPPORT OBLIGATION?

318
00:20:42,791 --> 00:20:44,524
WHEN WILL YOU SEE THEM?

319
00:20:44,593 --> 00:20:46,060
HAVE YOU SEEN THEM?

320
00:20:46,128 --> 00:20:48,540
I'LL GIVE THEM ALL THE
MAMAW THEY CAN STAND,

321
00:20:48,564 --> 00:20:50,530
BUT IF THEY HAVE NO DADDY...

322
00:20:50,599 --> 00:20:52,132
MOTHER.

323
00:20:52,201 --> 00:20:56,703
I SAT FOR MARILYN, FRIDAY LAST.

324
00:20:58,441 --> 00:20:59,773
HOW WERE THEY?

325
00:20:59,842 --> 00:21:01,241
WHAT DID THEY SAY?

326
00:21:03,545 --> 00:21:05,412
THEY WANTED TO KNOW

327
00:21:05,481 --> 00:21:07,714
WHEN YOU WERE COMING HOME.

328
00:21:29,805 --> 00:21:31,616
[Woman] <i>"DEAR MR. BARLOW,</i>

329
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:33,673
<i>"'THIS STORY CAME SO CLOSE.</i>

330
00:21:33,742 --> 00:21:35,909
<i>"WE HAD A 2-WEEK
BATTLE OVER IT HERE,</i>

331
00:21:35,978 --> 00:21:38,212
<i>"BUT YOU AND I LOST.</i>

332
00:21:38,280 --> 00:21:41,681
<i>"SO DID OUR READERS,
FEW THOUGH THEY BE.</i>

333
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:43,783
<i>"I DID WANT TO ASK
ABOUT THE TITLE.</i>

334
00:21:43,852 --> 00:21:45,552
<i>"NO ONE HERE WAS SURE WHAT</i>

335
00:21:45,621 --> 00:21:48,422
"WHITE GIRLS WITH BLACK
ASSES <i>ACTUALLY MEANT.</i>

336
00:21:48,491 --> 00:21:50,957
<i>"THE STORY REALLY
PUT SOME PEOPLE OFF.</i>

337
00:21:51,027 --> 00:21:53,994
<i>"IT'S THE STRONGEST
THING I'VE SEEN IN YEARS.</i>

338
00:21:54,063 --> 00:21:55,907
<i>"I'D NEVER TELL YOU
HOW TO WRITE, BUT</i>

339
00:21:55,931 --> 00:21:57,931
<i>"IF YOU CHANGE THE TITLE</i>

340
00:21:58,000 --> 00:22:00,401
<i>"ANOTHER MAGAZINE MIGHT BITE.</i>

341
00:22:00,469 --> 00:22:03,670
<i>"I'D LOVE TO SEE ANYTHING
ELSE YOU WANNA SEND.</i>

342
00:22:03,739 --> 00:22:07,174
<i>"PLEASE KEEP WRITING, AND DON'T
LET THIS BE DISAPPOINTING TO YOU.</i>

343
00:22:07,243 --> 00:22:08,575
<i>"YOU HAVE GREAT TALENT.</i>

344
00:22:08,644 --> 00:22:10,244
<i>"AND WITH MATERIAL LIKE THIS,</i>

345
00:22:10,312 --> 00:22:11,923
<i>"YOU WILL NEED GREAT STAMINA.</i>

346
00:22:11,947 --> 00:22:13,247
<i>"ALL WARMEST WISHES,</i>

347
00:22:13,315 --> 00:22:14,781
<i>"BETTI DELOREO."</i>

348
00:22:26,128 --> 00:22:27,594
