349
00:22:37,139 --> 00:22:38,305
HI, DADDY.

350
00:22:47,716 --> 00:22:49,783
HEY, WHAT'S UP?

351
00:22:49,851 --> 00:22:51,663
YOURS FOR THE REST
OF THE WEEKEND.

352
00:22:51,687 --> 00:22:52,919
WHAT?

353
00:22:52,988 --> 00:22:54,832
YOU PAYS YOUR MONEY,
YOU GETS YOUR KIDS.

354
00:22:54,856 --> 00:22:57,157
PAYS MY MONEY?

355
00:22:57,226 --> 00:23:01,361
GOD. NOT A CLUE WHEN YOU FUCK
UP, NOT A CLUE WHEN YOU DON'T.

356
00:23:01,430 --> 00:23:03,097
BILLS PAID.

357
00:23:03,165 --> 00:23:06,645
COURT ORDERS COMPLIED
WITH, LAWYERS PAID IN FULL.

358
00:23:07,203 --> 00:23:10,070
CHILD SUPPORT, 3 MONTHS' WORTH.

359
00:23:10,139 --> 00:23:14,208
100-DOLLAR BILLS IN A MANILA
ENVELOPE, UNDER THE DOOR.

360
00:23:14,276 --> 00:23:18,212
IS ANY OF THIS RINGING
A BELL, LEON? HELLO?

361
00:23:18,280 --> 00:23:20,647
DRUNKEN-DEBT-PAYERS-R-US.

362
00:23:22,017 --> 00:23:23,283
IT'S ALL RIGHT, HONEY.

363
00:23:25,087 --> 00:23:27,087
[Bells ringing]

364
00:23:32,128 --> 00:23:33,793
[Leon whispers] MONROE.

365
00:23:42,037 --> 00:23:44,216
OH, I GOT EXTRA
CLOTHES FOR BOTH OF 'EM

366
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:45,872
AND I GOT EXTRA UNDERWEAR

367
00:23:45,941 --> 00:23:47,274
AND ALISHA'S MEDICINE.

368
00:23:47,343 --> 00:23:49,823
SHE'S ON A NEW STEROID, SO
SHE NEEDS A LOT OF WATER.

369
00:23:49,878 --> 00:23:51,556
JUST REMEMBER TO
KEEP HER DRINKING.

370
00:23:51,580 --> 00:23:53,347
ALAN, YOU'RE GONNA
HELP WITH ALISHA, TOO.

371
00:23:53,415 --> 00:23:55,059
I LOVE YOU. BYE.
HAVE A GOOD TIME.

372
00:23:55,083 --> 00:23:57,284
