WHAT?

388
00:24:25,648 --> 00:24:26,780
HUH?

389
00:24:37,693 --> 00:24:40,060
Y'ALL CAN SLEEP IN
YOUR OWN ROOM TONIGHT,

390
00:24:40,128 --> 00:24:42,462
OR YOU CAN SLEEP
IN HERE WITH ME.

391
00:24:50,739 --> 00:24:52,239
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT.

392
00:24:52,308 --> 00:24:56,176
SO ONE DAY, A TRAIN
COME THROUGH THE WOODS.

393
00:24:57,813 --> 00:25:01,748
WILD BOY HISSED
TO ALL THE SNAKES.

394
00:25:01,817 --> 00:25:04,984
TOLD THEM TO LINE
UP ON THE RAILS.

395
00:25:05,053 --> 00:25:09,456
AND THE TRAIN COME
OFF ON NEW SNAKE TRACK.

396
00:25:10,759 --> 00:25:14,127
WHY, THE SNAKES
TOOK THEM ALL THE WAY

397
00:25:14,930 --> 00:25:16,663
THROUGH THE WOODS

398
00:25:18,534 --> 00:25:21,101
TO THE CAVE.

399
00:25:21,169 --> 00:25:24,170
WELL, WILD BOY CALLED OUT
TO HIS NUMBER ONE, MAGIC DOG.

400
00:25:24,240 --> 00:25:25,672
[Barks like a dog]

401
00:25:25,741 --> 00:25:27,419
AND OLD MAGIC DOG
COME RUNNING UP.

402
00:25:27,443 --> 00:25:31,245
WILD BOY SAID, "I'M GOING
TO TELL YOU THE PLAN."

403
00:25:31,313 --> 00:25:34,259
THEY WERE GOING TO TAKE ALL
THE COAL FROM THE COAL CAR,

404
00:25:34,283 --> 00:25:38,118
AND THE BEAR WOULD SQUEEZE
EVERY LUMP WITH A BIG STRONG PAW

405
00:25:38,186 --> 00:25:40,787
UNTIL THEY ALL
TURNED INTO DIAMONDS.

406
00:25:48,848 --> 00:25:51,994
HEY, DAD, ME AND MAGIC DOG
CAN RUN FASTER THAN A TRAIN!

407
00:25:52,018 --> 00:25:53,695
