BACKPACK AND HER NEBULIZER

428
00:26:52,578 --> 00:26:54,422
AND YOUR BACKPACK
AND PUT THEM IN THE CAR?

429
00:26:54,446 --> 00:26:57,181
GO DO THAT FOR MAMA, ALL RIGHT?

430
00:26:57,249 --> 00:26:59,094
DOES THAT DOG
HAVE ITS SHOTS, LEON?

431
00:26:59,118 --> 00:27:00,017
