EXTRA HOURS, ALL RIGHT?

442
00:27:17,970 --> 00:27:20,182
WELL, WHY DON'T YOU JUST
LET 'EM STAY? THEY GOT TO EAT.

443
00:27:20,206 --> 00:27:24,208
