449
00:27:32,985 --> 00:27:34,484
WELL, YOU... IS
SOMEBODY COMING OVER?

450
00:27:34,553 --> 00:27:35,597
WHAT?

451
00:27:35,621 --> 00:27:37,287
[Thunder claps]

452
00:27:37,356 --> 00:27:38,356
WHAT?

453
00:27:38,423 --> 00:27:39,601
ARE YOU SEEING SOMEBODY?

454
00:27:39,625 --> 00:27:41,892
OH, DON'T YOU DO
THIS. DON'T DO...

455
00:27:41,961 --> 00:27:46,496
YES. YES. I AM, I'M
SEEING SOMEBODY.

456
00:27:46,565 --> 00:27:48,766
[Whispers] I'M SEEING
A LOT OF HIM, TOO.

