00:42:08,410 --> 00:42:10,809
<i>OHHH... I LOVE HER.</i>

679
00:42:26,361 --> 00:42:27,704
[Velma] <i>SAYONARA.</i>

680
00:42:27,728 --> 00:42:29,808
SHE'S A HELL OF A DANCER.

681
00:42:30,031 --> 00:42:32,598
[Leon] <i>JUMP OUTSIDE.</i>

682
00:42:32,667 --> 00:42:36,902
DOWN THE WORMHOLE
PILGRIMAGE OF TIME

683
00:42:36,971 --> 00:42:40,473
AS TIME BENT BACK
AND TURNED ON ITSELF.

684
00:42:40,542 --> 00:42:43,543
COMET GAS FIERY
TRAIL OF EXHAUST.

685
00:42:43,611 --> 00:42:46,645
IT'S WAKE OF DARK ROWS
AND YOUR SEA RIVERS.

686
00:42:46,714 --> 00:42:50,249
ARE YOU LISTENING TO
ME? EARTH OF AMERICANS.

687
00:42:50,318 --> 00:42:52,051
DARK MOTHER!

688
00:42:52,120 --> 00:42:55,988
CROSSED YOUR WIDE SEA
OF AMERICA TO BE BORN.

689
00:42:57,825 --> 00:43:00,626
[Leon] <i>YOU KNOW
WHEN YOU'RE A KID</i>

690
00:43:00,695 --> 00:43:03,096
<i>DRIVING AT NIGHT
WITH YOUR FOLKS?</i>

691
00:43:03,164 --> 00:43:06,832
<i>YOU'RE LYING IN THE
BACK. YOU FEEL SO SAFE.</i>

692
00:43:07,602 --> 00:43:09,635
<i>THIS IS NOT LIKE THAT.</i>

693
00:43:11,639 --> 00:43:13,839
<i>THIS IS NOT LIKE THAT AT ALL.</i>

694
00:43:15,843 --> 00:43:17,843
