MY LADDER, BOBBY.</i>

695
00:43:20,014 --> 00:43:21,747
<i>WHERE'S VELMA?</i>

696
00:43:21,816 --> 00:43:22,948
[Man laughing]

697
00:43:24,252 --> 00:43:25,651
<i>WHERE'S VELMA?</i>

698
00:43:26,354 --> 00:43:28,253
[Monroe] <i>OHH!</i>

699
00:43:28,322 --> 00:43:29,882
[Monroe] SATURDAY!

700
00:43:30,525 --> 00:43:31,991
♪ [Radio music playing]

701
00:43:45,039 --> 00:43:46,759
[Leon] I'LL SEE YOU LATER.

702
00:44:10,331 --> 00:44:11,631
WELL,

703
00:44:12,867 --> 00:44:15,568
WE HAVE HAD A NICE LONG CHAT

704
00:44:15,637 --> 00:44:17,757
ON THE PORCH HERE, HAVEN'T WE?

705
00:44:19,340 --> 00:44:21,552
WE TALKED ABOUT THE
GARDEN CLUB MEETING

706
00:44:21,576 --> 00:44:23,208
I HAD TO CANCEL,

707
00:44:23,277 --> 00:44:26,323
ABOUT THE PHONE CALLS I
