00:48:59,854 --> 00:49:03,255
WE WENT OUT TO VEGAS TO
MAKE IT LEGAL ON THE CHEAP.

777
00:49:03,324 --> 00:49:05,558
WELL, SHE DIDN'T WANT
HER OLD MAN PULLING

778
00:49:05,626 --> 00:49:07,793
SOME CRAZY SHIT
DURING THE VOWS, AND

779
00:49:07,862 --> 00:49:11,029
I WAS GOING TO ASK YOU
TO STAND UP WITH ME, BUT...

780
00:49:11,098 --> 00:49:12,898
WHEN YOU'RE IN THE FUNERAL GAME,

781
00:49:12,967 --> 00:49:15,167
LIKE VELMA'S FAMILY, IT'S HARD
