783
00:49:17,204 --> 00:49:18,204
BUT NOW THIS PARTY...

784
00:49:18,238 --> 00:49:19,483
[Leon] SORRY,

785
00:49:19,507 --> 00:49:22,441
I CAN'T TAKE ANYTHING
