786
00:49:22,510 --> 00:49:24,109
WITH THAT HAT ON.

787
00:49:29,750 --> 00:49:30,750
[Sighs]

788
00:49:31,352 --> 00:49:32,751
SAID VOWS, HUH?

789
00:49:32,820 --> 00:49:35,253
YEAH, YEAH. I DID. NOW LOOK...

790
00:49:35,322 --> 00:49:37,556
NOPE, NOPE, CAN'T LOOK.

791
00:49:40,427 --> 00:49:41,794
I CAN'T EVEN SEE YOU.

792
00:49:44,331 --> 00:49:47,833
YOUR FACE IS SO SUNNY.

793
00:49:47,902 --> 00:49:49,635
SO EBULLIENT.

