795
00:49:53,674 --> 00:49:55,741
LITTLE DRINKING, LITTLE DANCING,

796
00:49:55,810 --> 00:49:57,643
LITTLE MARIACHI BAND.

797
00:49:57,712 --> 00:49:59,389
YOU CAN SLEEP IN
THE BARN LIKE YOU LIKE.

798
00:49:59,413 --> 00:50:01,246
I'M BUSY.

799
00:50:01,315 --> 00:50:04,383
LITTLE TECHNOLOGICAL
FIX TO A SPIRITUAL PROBLEM.

800
00:50:04,451 --> 00:50:06,162
WELL, THAT SOUNDS
REAL PROMISING.

