00:50:06,186 --> 00:50:08,988
WELL, NOTHING TO
IT, JUST A LITTLE...

802
00:50:09,056 --> 00:50:12,324
TINKERING, A LITTLE SOLITUDE,

803
00:50:12,393 --> 00:50:13,626
NAVEL-GAZING.

