00:50:20,434 --> 00:50:23,168
"MEN MET EACH OTHER
WITH ERECTED LOOK

805
00:50:23,237 --> 00:50:25,771
"THE STEPS WERE
HIGHER THAT THEY TOOK

806
00:50:25,840 --> 00:50:29,174
"FRIENDS TO CONGRATULATE
THEIR FRIENDS

807
00:50:30,044 --> 00:50:31,544
"MADE HASTE"

808
00:50:31,612 --> 00:50:35,714
THAT SHIT NEVER HAPPENED!
BUT THOSE WERE THE DAYS!

809
00:50:49,931 --> 00:50:51,597
INCOMING, BROTHER.

810
00:51:24,031 --> 00:51:26,832
♪ [Music playing on radio]

811
00:51:26,901 --> 00:51:30,769
