00:52:05,673 --> 00:52:07,305
<i>WHY IS THAT?</i>

823
00:52:11,078 --> 00:52:12,477
[Panting]

824
00:52:14,281 --> 00:52:15,748
[Coughs]

825
00:52:16,216 --> 00:52:17,282
OH.

826
00:52:17,351 --> 00:52:18,351
OH.

827
00:52:19,253 --> 00:52:20,485
THANK GOD.

828
00:52:21,155 --> 00:52:22,921
IT FELL OUT.

829
00:52:22,990 --> 00:52:24,623
DIDN'T EVEN KNOW.

