00:52:24,692 --> 00:52:27,660
TRUCK'S ON UP THE ROAD.
WENT TO TURN AROUND.

831
00:52:27,728 --> 00:52:31,730
RAN OUT OF GAS. FUCKING
STUPID! RUN BACK HERE.

832
00:52:31,799 --> 00:52:34,066
MUST HAVE BEEN HALF A MILE.

833
00:52:34,135 --> 00:52:36,035
YOU GONNA WATCH IT FOR ME?

834
00:52:36,103 --> 00:52:37,703
UH... NO.

835
